STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Erick BYICAZA, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0848 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 3, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Eric Byizaca appeals the judgment and sentence entered after he pled guilty to one count of dependent adult abuse. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
